#: ../content/index.rst:10
msgid "Description"
msgstr ""

#: ../content/index.rst:11
msgid "A detailed service catalog which enhances services with multilingual descriptions, assigns queues and ticket types to them, and lets the customer browse through them and directly create tickets for specific services on the customer dashboard. Additionally administration is simplified by providing options to set services as default services directly in the service, automatically create service specific ACLs, and much more."
msgstr ""

